{"name": "okxos", "metadata": {"name": "okxos", "version": "0.1.3", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/yourusername/okxos", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["httpx"], "summary": "A Python client for OKX OS APIs", "upload_time": 1732764393}, "documentation": ["# okxos\n\n`okxos` \u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u57fa\u4e8e OKX OS API \u7684 Python \u5f02\u6b65\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u5e93\uff0c\u4f7f\u7528 `httpx` \u5b9e\u73b0 HTTP \u8bf7\u6c42\u5c01\u88c5\uff0c\u652f\u6301 Wallet API\u3001DEX API\u3001Marketplace API \u548c DeFi API \u7684\u529f\u80fd\uff0c\u65e8\u5728\u4e3a\u5f00\u53d1\u8005\u63d0\u4f9b\u7b80\u4fbf\u5feb\u6377\u7684 Web3 \u5e94\u7528\u5f00\u53d1\u89e3\u51b3\u65b9\u6848\u3002\n\n## \u529f\u80fd\u7279\u6027\n\n- **Wallet API**: \u652f\u6301\u94fe\u67e5\u8be2\u3001\u5b9e\u65f6\u5e01\u4ef7\u3001\u4ee3\u5e01\u8f6c\u8d26\u7b49\u529f\u80fd\u3002\n- **DEX API**: \u652f\u6301\u94fe\u4fe1\u606f\u67e5\u8be2\u3001\u4ea4\u6613\u805a\u5408\u7b49\u529f\u80fd\u3002\n- **Marketplace API**: \u63d0\u4f9b NFT \u5e02\u573a\u529f\u80fd\uff08\u672a\u6765\u652f\u6301\uff09\u3002\n- **DeFi API**: \u67e5\u8be2\u534f\u8bae\u5217\u8868\u3001\u6295\u8d44\u4ea7\u54c1\u4fe1\u606f\u7b49\u3002\n\n## \u5b89\u88c5\n\n```bash\npip install okxos\n```\n\n## \u5feb\u901f\u5f00\u59cb\n```bash\nfrom okxos import OKXClient, WalletAPI, DEXAPI, MarketplaceAPI, DeFiAPI\n\n# \u521d\u59cb\u5316\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\nclient = OKXClient(\n    api_key=\"your_api_key\",\n    secret_key=\"your_secret_key\",\n    passphrase=\"your_passphrase\",\n    project_id=\"your_project_id\",\n)\n\n# \u521d\u59cb\u5316 WalletAPI\nwallet_api = WalletAPI(client)\n# \u8c03\u7528 WalletAPI \u83b7\u53d6\u652f\u6301\u7684\u94fe\u5217\u8868\nresult = wallet_api.get_supported_chains()\n\n# \u521d\u59cb\u5316 DEXAPI\ndex_api = DEXAPI(client)\n# \u8c03\u7528 DEXAPI \u83b7\u53d6\u6307\u5b9a\u94fe\u4e0a\u7684\u6240\u6709\u5e01\u79cd\u5217\u8868\nresult = dex_api.get_all_tokens(chain_id=\"1\")\n\n# \u521d\u59cb\u5316 MarketplaceAPI\nmarketplace_api = MarketplaceAPI(client)\n# \u8c03\u7528 MarketplaceAPI \u83b7\u53d6\u5408\u96c6\u4fe1\u606f\nresult = marketplace_api.get_collection_info(runes_id=\"1\")\n\n# \u521d\u59cb\u5316 DeFiAPI\ndefi_api = DeFiAPI(client)\n# \u8c03\u7528 DeFiAPI \u83b7\u53d6\u652f\u6301\u7684\u534f\u8bae\u5217\u8868\nresult = defi_api.get_protocol_list()\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "okxos.wallet", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "okxos.wallet.WalletAPI", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "okxos.wallet.WalletAPI.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "client", "type": {"name": "OKXClient", "xref": {"fqname": "okxos.okxos.client.OKXClient", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "okxos.wallet.WalletAPI.get_supported_chains", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u67e5\u8be2\u652f\u6301\u7684\u533a\u5757\u94fe\n\n\u5b98\u65b9\u6587\u6863: https://www.okx.com/zh-hans/web3/build/docs/waas/walletapi-api-get-supported-blockchain", "\u67e5\u8be2\u652f\u6301\u7684\u533a\u5757\u94fe api/v5/wallet/chain/supported-chains"]}, {"name": "okxos.wallet.WalletAPI.get_current_prices", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token_data_list", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u83b7\u53d6\u6307\u5b9a\u4ee3\u5e01\u7684\u5f53\u524d\u4ef7\u683c\n\n\u5b98\u65b9\u6587\u6863: <https://www.okx.com/zh-hans/web3/build/docs/waas/walletapi-api-get-current-pricelist>\n\n```\nparam token_data_list\n\n\u5305\u542b\u4ee3\u5e01\u4fe1\u606f\u7684\u5217\u8868\uff0c\u6bcf\u4e2a\u5143\u7d20\u4e3a\u5b57\u5178\uff0c\u683c\u5f0f\u5982\u4e0b\uff1a\n[\n\nsource:7: (ERROR/3) Unexpected indentation.\n\n{\"chainIndex\": \"1\", \"tokenAddress\": \"0xc18360217d8f7ab5e7c516566761ea12ce7f9d72\"},\n{\"chainIndex\": \"0\", \"tokenAddress\": \"btc-brc20-ordi\"}\n\nsource:9: (WARNING/2) Block quote ends without a blank line; unexpected unindent.\n\nsource:9: (INFO/1) Unexpected possible title overline or transition.\nTreating it as ordinary text because it's so short.\n\n]\n\nreturn\n\n\u5b9e\u65f6\u4ef7\u683c\u4fe1\u606f\u7684 JSON \u6570\u636e\n```\n"]}, {"name": "okxos.wallet.WalletAPI.get_historical_prices", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "chain_index", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token_address", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "limit", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "cursor", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "begin", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "end", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "period", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u67e5\u8be2\u67d0\u4e2a\u5e01\u79cd\u7684\u5386\u53f2\u4ef7\u683c\n\n\u5b98\u65b9\u6587\u6863: <https://www.okx.com/zh-hans/web3/build/docs/waas/walletapi-api-get-historical-pricelist>\n\n```\nparam chain_index\n\n\u94fe\u552f\u4e00\u6807\u8bc6\u3002\n\nparam token_address\n\n\u4ee3\u5e01\u5730\u5740\u6216\u6807\u8bc6\u7b26\uff0c\u53ef\u9009\u3002\n\nparam limit\n\n\u6bcf\u6b21\u67e5\u8be2\u8fd4\u56de\u7684\u6761\u6570\uff0c\u9ed8\u8ba4 50\uff0c\u6700\u5927 200\u3002\n\nparam cursor\n\n\u6e38\u6807\u4f4d\u7f6e\uff0c\u9ed8\u8ba4\u4e3a\u7b2c\u4e00\u4e2a\u3002\n\nparam begin\n\n\u67e5\u8be2\u665a\u4e8e\u8be5\u65f6\u95f4\u7684\u5386\u53f2\u5e01\u4ef7\uff0c\u5355\u4f4d\u6beb\u79d2\u65f6\u95f4\u6233\u3002\n\nparam end\n\n\u67e5\u8be2\u65e9\u4e8e\u8be5\u65f6\u95f4\u7684\u5386\u53f2\u5e01\u4ef7\uff0c\u5355\u4f4d\u6beb\u79d2\u65f6\u95f4\u6233\u3002\n\nparam period\n\n\u65f6\u95f4\u95f4\u9694\u5355\u4f4d\uff0c\u652f\u6301 1m, 5m, 30m, 1h, 1d\uff0c\u9ed8\u8ba4\u503c\u4e3a 1d\u3002\n\nreturn\n\n\u5386\u53f2\u5e01\u4ef7\u7684 JSON \u6570\u636e\u3002\n```\n"]}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "okxos.defi", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "okxos.defi.DeFiAPI", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "okxos.defi.DeFiAPI.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "client", "type": {"name": "OKXClient", "xref": {"fqname": "okxos.okxos.client.OKXClient", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "okxos.defi.DeFiAPI.get_protocol_list", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "platform_id", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "platform_name", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u67e5\u8be2\u534f\u8bae\u5217\u8868\n\n\u5b98\u65b9\u6587\u6863: <https://www.okx.com/zh-hans/web3/build/docs/waas/defi-api-reference-explore-protocol-list>\n\n```\nparam platform_id\n\n\u5e73\u53f0 ID\uff0c\u53ef\u9009\u3002\n\nparam platform_name\n\n\u5e73\u53f0\u5b98\u65b9\u540d\u79f0\uff0c\u53ef\u9009\u3002\n\nreturn\n\n\u534f\u8bae\u4fe1\u606f\u7684 JSON \u6570\u636e\u3002\n```\n"]}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "okxos.client", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "okxos.client.OKXClient", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "okxos.client.OKXClient.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "api_key", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "secret_key", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "passphrase", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "project_id", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "ba